---
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Head from '../components/Head.astro';
---

<html lang="en">
	<Head title="About"/>
	<body class="bg-gray-200">	
		<Navbar/>
		<section class="container mx-auto p-6">
			<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">About Us</h1>
			<p class="mb-4">
				Welcome to Property Hub! We are dedicated to helping you find the perfect property that suits your needs. 
				Our team of experienced professionals is here to guide you through every step of the process.
			</p>
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Our Mission</h2>
			<p class="mb-4">
				Our mission is to provide exceptional service and expertise in the real estate market. We strive to make 
				the buying and selling process as smooth and stress-free as possible.
			</p>
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Our Team</h2>
			<p class="mb-4">
				Our team consists of knowledgeable and passionate individuals who are committed to helping you achieve your 
				real estate goals. We pride ourselves on our integrity, professionalism, and dedication to our clients.
			</p>
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Contact Us</h2>
			<p>
				If you have any questions or would like to learn more about our services, please don't hesitate to 
				<a href="/property-hub/contact" class="text-blue-500 underline">contact us</a>. We look forward to working with you!
			</p>
		</section>
	</body>
</html>
